376
00:27:51,439 --> 00:27:54,640
Tentu saja. Patah hati,

377
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:57,280
hanya bisa disembuhkan saat fisikmu bekerja keras.

378
00:27:57,509 --> 00:28:00,219
Konon, pertengkaran pasangan cepat berlalu.

379
00:28:00,219 --> 00:28:03,590
Jak Doo sudah dua pekan di sini.

380
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:06,759
