415
00:29:36,949 --> 00:29:38,820
Haruskah kita bertindak

416
00:29:38,820 --> 00:29:40,320
untuk menghentikan pertengkaran mereka?

417
00:29:40,350 --> 00:29:42,489
Haruskah kita bertindak?

